---------------------------------------------------
[spell]: Unseen Servant
[level]: 2nd Lvl Conjuration
[cost] : 30 sp
[type] : none
[delay]: none
---------------------------------------------------
Create a magical servant to carry an item for you.
The servant will deliver one item to another
player, or take it to the shop to be sold.
Use 'userv <item> <player>' 
or 'userv <item> shop' to cast.
---------------------------------------------------

